OL,3,CCrucial rescue window narrows as
OL,4,CVenezuela enters third day after
OL,5,Cdeadly quakes
OL,7,FThe situation has grown increasingly
OL,8,Fdesperate in Venezuela as people
OL,9,Fcontinue to dig through the rubble of
OL,10,Fcollapsed homes, three days after two
OL,11,Fearthquakes hit the country.
OL,13,FMore than 920 people have been killed
OL,14,Fafter 7.2 and 7.5 magnitude quakes
OL,15,Fstruck the country within minutes of
OL,16,Feach other on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
