CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782689571
OL,3,CCrucial rescue window narrows as
OL,4,CVenezuela enters third day after
OL,5,Cdeadly quakes
OL,7,FIt is believed that the death toll
OL,8,Ffigure will continue to climb in the
OL,9,Fcoming days, with some 3,360 people
OL,10,Finjured and time running out to find
OL,11,Fsurvivors.
OL,13,FA 68-strong search-and-rescue team,
OL,14,Fincluding specialist dogs, is expected
OL,15,Fto arrive in Venezuela from the UK on
OL,16,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
