OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782689571
OL,3,CCrucial rescue window narrows as
OL,4,CVenezuela enters third day after
OL,5,Cdeadly quakes
OL,7,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,8,F"We are making immediately available
OL,9,F#2 million of emergency humanitarian
OL,10,Fassistance, so that we can get search
OL,11,Fand rescue teams into Venezuela, so
OL,12,Fthat we can do full assessments of the
OL,13,Fdamage that's been done.
OL,15,F"We're also working with the United
OL,16,FStates, with Canada, with the United
OL,17,FNations, and making sure that we can
OL,18,Fget support in for Venezuela, for the
OL,19,Fpeople who need our help."
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
