PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782689571
OL,3,CCrucial rescue window narrows as
OL,4,CVenezuela enters third day after
OL,5,Cdeadly quakes
OL,7,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer added: "My
OL,8,Fthoughts are with the people of
OL,9,FVenezuela following this week's
OL,10,Fdevastating earthquakes. The UK stands
OL,11,Fin solidarity with all those affected,
OL,12,Fparticularly those who have lost loved
OL,13,Fones, homes and livelihoods."
OL,15,FVenezuelan authorities announced on
OL,16,FFriday night that they would block
OL,17,Faccess to La Guaira, the epicentre of
OL,18,Fthe destruction, as chaos and traffic
OL,19,Fnoise began to hinder search efforts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
