OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782689571
OL,3,CCrucial rescue window narrows as
OL,4,CVenezuela enters third day after
OL,5,Cdeadly quakes
OL,7,FOfficials said anyone who wants to
OL,8,Fenter would now have to seek official
OL,9,Fpermits, but provided few details of
OL,10,Fwho would be allowed in.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, Venezuelans took the search
OL,13,Ffor missing loved ones into their own
OL,14,Fhands, citing a scarcity of government
OL,15,Frescuers.
OL,17,FPeople reported seeing few state
OL,18,Frescue teams in the hardest-hit areas,
OL,19,Fdespite authorities projecting an
OL,20,Fimage of a robust government response.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
