OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782689571
OL,3,CCrucial rescue window narrows as
OL,4,CVenezuela enters third day after
OL,5,Cdeadly quakes
OL,7,F"We are not going to hide absolutely
OL,8,Fanything about the magnitude of this
OL,9,Ftragedy", he added.
OL,11,FAuthorities said they have rescued 243
OL,12,Fpeople.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, The International
OL,15,FOrganization for Migration said up to
OL,16,F6.76 million people could have been
OL,17,Faffected, some 2 million of them in
OL,18,Fthe capital Caracas alone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
