OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782689571
OL,3,CCrucial rescue window narrows as
OL,4,CVenezuela enters third day after
OL,5,Cdeadly quakes
OL,7,FThe destruction was amplified by the
OL,8,Fquick succession of shallow quakes,
OL,9,Fexperts said. Many continued to sleep
OL,10,Fon the streets on Friday night as a
OL,11,Fresult.
OL,13,FGovernment forces distributed food and
OL,14,Fwater to survivors in La Guaira, just
OL,15,Fnorth of the capital, Caracas, and
OL,16,Facting President Delcy Rodriguez said
OL,17,Fher government was mounting a full
OL,18,Fresponse during these "critical hours
OL,19,Ffor rescuing people alive."
OL,26,@xD@\rt
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
