OL,3,CCrucial rescue window narrows as
OL,4,CVenezuela enters third day after
OL,5,Cdeadly quakes
OL,7,FAlmost 48 hours since the deadly
OL,8,Fdouble earthquake in Venezuela and the
OL,9,Fdeath toll continues to rise as rescue
OL,10,Foperations arrive in country, as ITV
OL,11,FNews Correspondents Robert Moore and
OL,12,FJohn Ray report
OL,14,FThe acting President welcomed the
OL,15,Farrival of international rescuers and
OL,16,Fhumanitarian aid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
