OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782689571
OL,3,CCrucial rescue window narrows as
OL,4,CVenezuela enters third day after
OL,5,Cdeadly quakes
OL,7,FVenezuelan authorities said Friday
OL,8,Fthat 861 volunteers from Mexico, the
OL,9,FUS, El Salvador, Switzerland, Colombia
OL,10,Fand beyond were in the country, and
OL,11,Fmore were coming from elsewhere.
OL,13,FRodriguez said she spoke to US
OL,14,FPresident Donald Trump and Secretary
OL,15,Fof State Marco Rubio on Friday, and
OL,16,Fthat they reaffirmed their commitment
OL,17,Fto send rescue teams and aid equipment.
OL,26,@uD@Ert
